					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p123187">Gameboy SRAM Copier</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=123187&amp;sid=d2f992d2413ec8ff7b68bb2661d62d19#p123187"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Thu Jan 02, 2014 10:04 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
