						<div class="postbody">I finally got my EMS-64M flashcart. It turns out that the EMS 64M always resets the gameboy when it is inserted. So, this works for copying saved data to a cartridge, but not the other way around. I may work on a solution involving the link cable, as nitro2k01 suggested.</div>

