				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You can stick in a GB cartridge while running a multiboot mode program with all interrupts disabled, and it will reboot into GB mode and run the game (Warning, inserting GB cartridges into a running system may corrupt the saved game).  No ARM code or GBA BIOS code is responsible for it switching modes.</div>

					
